llm-wiki-plugin
Copyright 2026 Andrew Staker

This project implements and extends ideas described in Andrej Karpathy's “LLM Wiki” pattern:
https://gist.github.com/karpathy/442a6bf555914893e9891c11519de94f

Its interchange support targets Google Cloud's Open Knowledge Format (OKF) v0.1:
https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/knowledge-catalog/blob/main/okf/SPEC.md

Those works are acknowledged as conceptual lineage and specifications. Their names do not imply
endorsement. This distribution does not bundle their source code.
